Target: OntoService is designed to represent the terms, conditions, and obligations associated with service delivery as well as the execution details.

Comment: A classifier that indicates the current state of an event during a contract lifecycle
Label: Event status

Comment: A service that acts as a point of contact for communication, support, or assistance.
Label: Contact service

Comment: A monetary charge that is based on a well-known measurable unit. This charge varies according to the specific metrics such as weight, distance, or volumes with lower and upper bounds.
Label: Variable fee

Comment: A phase in the lifecycle for an agreement governing some service.
Label: Service agreement lifecycle stage

Comment: A kind of event that occurs during one or more stages of the lifecycle of an agreement that governs a service.
Label: Service agreement lifecycle event

Comment: A relationship describing the contact point for another service.
Label: serves as contact for

Comment: A relationship describing the service location, typically a point, within the building or site.
Label: has service location

Comment: specifies a scheduled time that can be associated with any element
